==Galician==
===Etymology===
Inherited, from a {{inh|gl|VL.|*sēperāre}} (or {{m|la||*ex-sēperāre}}), from {{inh|gl|la|sēparāre}}, present active infinitive of {{m|la|sēparō|t=I separate}}, from {{af|la|sē-|t1=apart|parō|t2=prepare|nocat=1}}. Compare {{cog|ast|dixebrar}}, {{cog|osp|xebrar}}, {{m|osp|exebrar}}, {{m|osp|dessebrar}}, {{cog|oc|sebrar}}, {{cog|fr|sevrer}}. {{doublet|gl|separar}}, a borrowing.
